    <briefdescription>
<para>Runtime PM info for device with synchronous PM. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Synchronous PM can be used with devices which suspend and resume operations can be performed in the critical section as they are short and non-blocking. Runtime PM API can be used from any context in that case. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
